## WASM 指令支持现状

### 已实现 ✓
- 控制流: unreachable, nop, block, loop, if, else, end, br, br_if, br_table, return, call
- 参数: drop, select
- 变量: local.get, local.set, local.tee, global.get, global.set
- 内存: i32.load, i32.store, i32.load8_s/u, i32.load16_s/u, i32.store8, i32.store16, memory.size, memory.grow
- 常量: i32.const (有符号LEB128)
- i32比较: eqz, eq, ne, lt_s/u, gt_s/u, le_s/u, ge_s/u
- i32算术: add, sub, mul, div_s/u, rem_s/u, and, or, xor, shl, shr_s/u

